---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Pork Rissoles with Sesame Fries & Asian Slaw
description: How to improve pork rissoles? Toss them in our mild Sichuan garlic paste, of course! It adds loads of flavour and that saucy touch
that makes every mouthful a delight. Fries with crisp sesame seeds and slaw coated in Japanese dressing seal the deal
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sichuan-glazed-pork-rissoles-291d9f2d.jpg
